Class PersistentRTreeJsi

java.lang.Object
  com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.spatialindex.PersistentRTreeJsi
All Implemented Interfaces:
INearestNeighbourFinder, IPersistentSpatialIndex, ISpatialIndex
public class PersistentRTreeJsi
extends java.lang.Object
implements IPersistentSpatialIndex, INearestNeighbourFinder, ISpatialIndex

Persistent spatial index which can resolve nearest neighbour queries.
To use: PersistentRTreeJsi sptidx = new PersistentRtreeJsi("/home/kk"); if(sptidx.exists()) sptidx.load(); sptidx.add(rect, int); ... sptidx.add(rect2,int2); sptidx.flush();
